Model 1 with all variables

df <- read.csv('Data/data_train.csv')
x_axis1=df[c(1)]
df<-df[ -c(1) ]
row.names(df) <- unlist(x_axis1, use.names=FALSE)
df$enginesize <-log(df$enginesize)
mod1 <- lm(price~.+compressionratio*fueltype,data=df)
summary(mod1)
